Sentencas: A textured layer of a highly conductive mixed ion-electron conductor, Pr4Ni3O10, with a layer structure is applicable as a cathode to intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells because of the large anisotropy in its conduction properties.
Titulo: Fabrication of high performance Pr4Ni3O10 cathode based upon magnetic orientation behavior for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: In the present work, an ab-plane preferentially oriented Pr4Ni3O10 cathode was successfully fabricated on a Gd2O3-doped CeO2 electrolyte using a magnetic orientation process in a 0.9 T magnetic field.
Titulo: Fabrication of high performance Pr4Ni3O10 cathode based upon magnetic orientation behavior for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The orientation of the Pr4Ni3O10 cathode effectively reduced not only the ohmic loss but also the polarization loss.
Titulo: Fabrication of high performance Pr4Ni3O10 cathode based upon magnetic orientation behavior for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cell
